### **Block Categories**
- **Layout Blocks**: User-editable components with business logic (NavBlock, FooterBlock, ContentGrids)
- **Module Blocks**: Content-specific components (ProductHero, PostBasic, FeatureCarousel)
- **Admin Blocks**: Management interfaces for all content types
- **UI Components**: Pure presentation components without business logic

